divs: Sighting DetailsI was sunbathing at a pool. When I looked up I clearly saw a pulse jet with "a string of pearl like" white contrail. I am an amateur astronomer and I know how to identify objects. I have never seen anything like it before. I was kicking myself because I had no camera. There was also a commercial airliner near by and its contrail was normal, so I know it wasn't from upper winds.
